HEADWORD: Haloed
<hw>Ha"loed</hw> <pr>(h⟦amac⟧"l⟦omac⟧d)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Surrounded with a halo; invested with an ideal glory;
glorified.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some <qex>haloed</qex> face bending over me.</q> <rj><qau>C.
